"title": "1613: Scripture, purpose of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1613",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture has been given by God to lead people to faith and salvation. Through Scripture believers are nurtured in faith and led to spiritual maturity.</p>\n<h2>Scripture is intended to lead people to salvation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14-2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:14–3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:11\">PSA 19:7–19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:30-John20:31\">JHN 20:30–20:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:8\">ROM 10:8</a></p>\n<h2>Scripture is intended to lead believers to maturity in faith</h2>\n<h3>By its teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:6-Deut6:9\">DEU 6:6–6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:8\">PSA 19:7–19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:9\">PSA 119:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>By its rebuke and correction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:11-Ps19:13\">PSA 19:11–19:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:11-1Cor10:12\">1CO 10:11–10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:12-Heb4:13\">HEB 4:12–4:13</a></p>\n<h3>By training in righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:29\">DEU 29:29</a></p>\n<h3>By its illumination</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:105\">PSA 119:105</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:8\">1JN 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>By its encouragement and reassurance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:13\">1JN 5:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:8-Ps19:9\">PSA 19:8–19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:50-Ps119:51\">PSA 119:50–119:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:76\">PSA 119:76</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:6\">HEB 12:5–12:6</a></p>\n<h3>By its record of God's promises</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:140\">PSA 119:140</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:25\">EZK 12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:44\">LUK 24:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:19-2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:19–1:22</a></p>\n<h3>By its trustworthiness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:24\">1KI 17:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:11\">PSA 19:7–19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:4\">PSA 33:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:151\">PSA 119:151</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:160\">PSA 119:160</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:24\">JHN 21:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:5\">REV 21:5</a></p>\n<h2>Scripture is essential for spiritual growth and maturity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1-Ps1:3\">PSA 1:1–1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:4\">MAT 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:5-John15:8\">JHN 15:5–15:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:17\">JHN 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10-Eph6:17\">EPH 6:10–6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:14–3:17</a></p>",
